This project includes color system mapping data (palettes/color-system-mapping.json)
derived from the Zippland/perler-beads project:

  https://github.com/Zippland/perler-beads
  Commit: 2efee730f73dd4eb472ebde443a022d11f98bc21
  Obtained: 2026-07-01

The mapping data is used as-is with format adjustments (pulled into
JSON file structure) to support the MARD / COCO / 漫漫 / 盼盼 / 咪小窝
color system display. No structural changes were made to the hex-to-code
mappings themselves.

